data.description:
This secluded home sits on a tranquil 5+ acre wooded lot, providing a serene private retreat. With four bedrooms, three full baths, an upstairs loft, and ample storage, this spacious and inviting residence is ideal for gatherings. You can stay warm by the fire during colder months and savor a cup of coffee on the back patio while observing the local wildlife in the summer. The back porch includes a slab ready for a hot tub or jacuzzi, along with RV hookups. The expansive yard offers endless possibilities for customization, featuring a meandering wet weather creek at the front and lush vegetation throughout. Adventure abounds here!

In the Mountain Lakes Ranch community, you'll be treated to breathtaking views and a range of amenities, including two mountain lakes for fishing and recreation, a clubhouse, swimming pool, walking paths, a playground, and more.
